queries.query: INSERT INTO `api_accesslogs` (`vIPAddress`, `vAPIName`, `vAPIURL`, `dAccessDate`, `vPlatform`, `vBrowser`, `vFileName`) VALUES ('103.47.153.165', 'get_message_list', 'http://18.211.58.235/canoodle/WS/get_message_list', '2020-11-18 12:57:29', 'Unknown OS Platform', 'Unknown Browser', 'get_message_list-1605704249.json')

SELECT `m`.`iMessageId` AS `message_id`,`m`.`iSenderId` AS `sender_id`,`m`.`iReceiverId` AS `receiver_id`,`m`.`vMessage` AS `message`,concat(u.vFirstName," ",u.vLastName) AS sender_name,concat(u1.vFirstName," ",u1.vLastName) AS receiver_name,`m`.`dtModifiedDate` AS `updated_at`,('') AS sender_image,('') AS receiver_image,('') AS connection_type_by_logged_user,('') AS connection_type_by_receiver_user FROM `message` AS `m` LEFT JOIN `users` AS `u` ON `m`.`iSenderId` = `u`.`iUserId` LEFT JOIN `users` AS `u1` ON `m`.`iReceiverId` = `u1`.`iUserId` WHERE (m.iSenderId = '12' OR m.iReceiverId = '12')   ORDER BY `m`.`dtAddedDate` DESC

SELECT '' AS connection_type,                          (SELECT eConnectionType                          FROM user_connections                          WHERE eStatus='active' AND iUserId=12 AND  iConnectionUserId = 13) AS connection_type_by_logged_user,                         (SELECT eConnectionResult                          FROM user_connections                          WHERE eStatus='active' AND iUserId=12 AND  iConnectionUserId = 13) AS connection_result_by_logged_user,                         (SELECT eConnectionType                          FROM user_connections                          WHERE eStatus='active' AND iUserId=13 AND  iConnectionUserId = 12) AS connection_type_by_receiver_user,                         (SELECT eConnectionResult                          FROM user_connections                          WHERE eStatus='active' AND iUserId=13 AND  iConnectionUserId = 12) AS connection_result_by_receiver_user                                                  FROM user_connections LIMIT 1

SELECT '' AS connection_type,                          (SELECT eConnectionType                          FROM user_connections                          WHERE eStatus='active' AND iUserId=12 AND  iConnectionUserId = 1) AS connection_type_by_logged_user,                         (SELECT eConnectionResult                          FROM user_connections                          WHERE eStatus='active' AND iUserId=12 AND  iConnectionUserId = 1) AS connection_result_by_logged_user,                         (SELECT eConnectionType                          FROM user_connections                          WHERE eStatus='active' AND iUserId=1 AND  iConnectionUserId = 12) AS connection_type_by_receiver_user,                         (SELECT eConnectionResult                          FROM user_connections                          WHERE eStatus='active' AND iUserId=1 AND  iConnectionUserId = 12) AS connection_result_by_receiver_user                                                  FROM user_connections LIMIT 1
